data.real_title: Luckies of London | Scratch Map Original Edition | World Map Scratch Art | Scratch Off Map | World Map Wall Art | The Original Scratch Map Creators |
data.real_desc: The Original Scratch Map – Conceived in 2009 by Luckies of London, the innovators of the Scratch off Map.  Highest quality Scratch Maps – As the creator of the Scratch off Map concept, we pride ourselves in manufacturing the finest quality scratcable maps on the market. Each map is made using premium quality materials, intricate geographical design crafted by our highly skilled team of cartographers and featuring our easy to scratch off top foil layer.  Largest collection of Scratch Maps – Due to the enormous success of the Original Scratch Map in 2009, since then the collection has grown into many different Scratch off Maps, from region specific to compact travel and large wall maps.  Scratch Map as a gift - Each Scratch Map comes in it’s own sturdy cardboard tube, perfect for sending to someone as a gift or strong and protecting your map. There’s a Scratch Map for everyone, why not browse through our extensive collection.  Scratch Map is the perfect way to show off where you've been travelling while livening up your wall with a colourful world map. Scratch Map is a uber-massive wall map, featuring a gold top foil layer. Why? Because you get a unique, slick looking gold wall map to start with, and then scratch off all the places you've visited to reveal a whole new world below, featuring colour and geographical detail. The result is a totally unique and personalised world map. The perfect travel gift for anyone you know jetting off. Comes packaged in a tube. This 81.9 x 58.2 cm world map is based on the idea of the scratch card so you just scratch off the places you've been and bright colours will be revealed underneath. Scratch Map also includes facts about certain countries and cities. Fun for all the family.  BEWARE OF FAKES SCRATCH MAPS – Unfortunately there are many fake Scratch of maps available on the market today. They’re made using inferior materials, poor design and poor-quality foil. Our maps are manufactured to the highest standard with our secret formula easy to scratch top foil layer. Our maps also have a premium quality multi coloured laminate underneath, no other map comes close and we know as we’ve tested them all. To avoid disappointment, by from a Luckies of London Amazon listing. The Original Scratch Off Map Introducing the world’s most unique travel essential, the Scratch off Map! The Scratch off Map was conceived in 2009 by Luckies of London, a world-renowned gifts designer and manufacturer. The Scratch off Map features a scratchable top foil layer that covers the maps surface, a premium foil that’s easily removed with a coin or an eraser. The idea is to scratch off where you’ve been to reveal the map underneath the foil layer and create a personalized, interactive travel record. The top foil coating features a map of the world design in gold on a high quality durable laminated thick card. As you scratch off the foil, a new bright, multi coloured world is revealed, bringing your travels to life!  Highly detailed scratchable map of the world  This highly detailed Scratch off Map of the World boasts a generous amount of detail. The map is separated into continents with countries featuring state lines, borders, cities, capitals, towns and more. An excellent resource for geography, fun for kids too as they learn more about the earth with a visual interactive approach. The different colours help identify the many different regions, terrains and various areas. This fine piece of cartography also features islands, colonies and Oceans. At the base of the map is a legend showing the various scales, gradients, travel trivia and more. Created, design and manufactured by Luckies of London  At Luckies of London we pride ourselves in manufacturing the finest Scratch off Maps on offer, the original and by far the best. The attention to detail with each design combined with the signature scratch off foil are what makes all our maps the pinnacle in interactive cartography.  Record your travels with a personalized world travel map  Whether you’re an island hoping explorer, someone who’s’ backpacked across Asia or a frequent flyer, this map is for you! Create your own personalized visual travel journal of places you’ve visited for all to see. The Scratch off Map Original has a boundless range of uses, you can also create a visual travel itinerary for journeys and adventure that will motivate, a must for the wanderlust!  To enjoy the Scratch off Map and use to it’s full potential, simply roll out and fasten the edges with low tack sticky tape to avoid damage or use paper weights to secure the edges. Then gently scratch off the foil with a small coin or an eraser and discover the world from a whole new perspective.  The enormous success of the Scratch off Map spawned a comprehensive collection of scratchable maps. This extensive range now features a compact Travel Map edition, Deluxe, Platinum, Rose Gold, and regions specific maps such as Scratch off Map Europe, USA and U.K. plus large Scratch off Maps.
